# Temp difference = 1150 K - 270 K = 880 K
# Total time taken for cooling = timestep x no of iterations in quenched step = (0.002 x 10000) ps
# So cooling rate = 880 K / (0.002 x 10000) ps = 4.4x10^13 K/s for the above in.file
